      "id": 1,
      "text": "Roessleville takes its name from German immigrant Theophilus Roessle, who arrived in 1825 and turned the area into a celery‑producing hub.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        2,
        3,
        26
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
